Cell.Text: [S] G'day captain! I got the boys on deck and prepin' yer new ship. | She'll be ready to go on her first voyage with ya soon, | so if you have any unfinished business or farewells you'd like to say, now's as good a time as any captain! | I'll be here waiting for ya when yer ready to set sail.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_MeetingGibbsBranchTopic: Gibbs, how's the preparation goin'?

Cell.Text: I don't mean to sound disrespectful captain, but you should probably have walk around and see if you have anyone you wanna say yer farewells to.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_NoFarewellsBranchTopic: Are we ready mate?

Cell.Text: Aye.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Stay: Alright, I'll get right on that.

Cell.Text: [S] Aye aye captain! If ye say so, though yer probably gonna miss out on something.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Leave: I'd rather just leave now and be gone.

Cell.Text: You've said yer farewells then? Everything's good I hope?

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_FarewellsGoodTopic: I think I'm just about ready

Cell.Text: I hear ya! By the way, did ye happen to pick up any last minute supplies, sure would come in handy!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_GoodTerms: Aye, glad to be leavin' on good terms.

Cell.Text: I hear ya! By the way, did ye happen to pick up any last minute supplies, sure would come in handy!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_LetsGo: Yeah, just wanna get outta here though.

Cell.Text: [S] Brilliant! With all these extra supplies, voyage should be a bit more smooth! | And with you back now, we can finally set sail from this plague ridden land! All aboard!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_HasSupplies: Sure did, mate.

Cell.Text: [S] 'Tis a shame, but we got the basics so we should be fine. | Anyway, now that you're back son, we can set sail from this plague ridden land! All aboard!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_NoSupplies: No, I got nothin'.

Cell.Text: Captain? Everythin' alright with ye? 'Cause that's the face of someone who ate somethin' sour.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_FarewellsBadTopic: Gibbs, lets get outta here.

Cell.Text: [S] Alright captain, well cheer up, we're about to hit open waters in search of treasure and new land! | Besides, whatever happened at least ye got some extra grub there. | Anyway, now that you're back, let's set sail! All aboard!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_NotGoodTerms: Ain't leavin' on good terms.

Cell.Text: [S] Alright captain, well cheer up, we're about to hit open waters in search of treasure and new land! | Anyway, now that you're back, let's set sail! All aboard!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_NotTalking: Not gonna talk about it, Joshamee.

Cell.Text: Good man. I think your first mate was lookin' for ya though, you should probably have a chat with him.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_MeetingCainTopic: Cain, How's the dock holdin' up?

Cell.Text: Mornin' lad! You're finally setting sail on us then?

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_CainFarewellTopic: Cain, Just here to pay my dues.

Cell.Text: Ah well why don't you head over to my house over by the gate? I had some food rations packed up for ya! You'll find them in the chest downstairs. | Might give you somethin' to remember me by, eh? I'm sure you can return the favour when you're back.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_CainGoodFarewell: Aye, gonna miss folks alright.

Cell.Text: [S] Anyway lad, I don't want to keep ya, I know you need to be off. I wish you fair sailing and I hope to see you again soon!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Returning: Of course! I'll return with riches from foreign lands! Thanks again friend!

Cell.Text: [S] Anyway lad, I don't want to keep ya, I know you need to be off. I wish you fair sailing and I hope to see you again soon!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_NoReturn: Oh yeah... when I return, right.

Cell.Text: Oi, no need to be so rude lad, was just trying to be nice. Besides, everyone 'round here knows today's the day you set off!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_CainBadFarewell: That's really none of your business.

Cell.Text: Ah well why don't you head over to my house over by the gate? I had some food rations packed up for ya! You'll find 'em in the chest downstairs. | Might give you somethin' to remember me by, eh? I'm sure you can return the favour when you're back.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Nervous: Sorry, just a wee bit nervous is all.

Cell.Text: [S] There's no need for any of that now. I think you should be off.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_GoodRiddance: Good riddance to the nosy lot of em!

Cell.Text: You'd best set off lad while the winds are still favourable. Don't forget the food I got for you either!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_CainGoodEndTopic: Cain.

Cell.Text: I think you should leave.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_CainBadEndTopic: Cain.

Cell.Text: Listen captain, a lot of the crew are starting to get a wee bit uneasy. | Rumours are a spreadin' and some are beginnin' to think that you don't know where we're goin' anymore. | 'Course aye meself don't believe 'em sir but some are dreadin' that we're lost at sea.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_MeetingGibbsShipTopic: Gibbs, what's today's report?

Cell.Text: [S] Whatever the case, they're becoming worried and restless. I really think you should talk to them. | Maybe I'm even going a little crazy, my rum supply seems to be getting low fast, too fast for me even!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_OnCourse: I can assure you we are right on course!

Cell.Text: [S] Whatever the case, they're becoming worried and restless. I really think you should talk to them. | Maybe I'm even going a little crazy, my rum supply seems to be getting low fast, too fast for me even!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Lostish: Maybe they're right... I suppose.

Cell.Text: Have you talked to everyone yet? There's still some tension around the ship, and I still hear the crew have problems.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_NotDoneTopic: How's the crew holdin' up?

Cell.Text: [S] Sir, commotion has died down a lot. Everything seems a quiet, too quiet maybe?

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_DoneQuestsTopic: Right, I think I've sorted everyone.

Cell.Text: You've done the crew well captain. Most of everyone seems to have quietened down.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_GoodEnd: So how's the crew holdin' up now?

Cell.Text: [S] Something does feel a bit strange now that you mention it cap'n... | W-wait, do you hear that? I think there's something lurking in the waters!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Tense: Hmm, still seems a bit tense though...

Cell.Text: [S] Well done captain! But does something still feel a little strange to you? | W-wait, do you hear that? There's something lurking in the waters!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Pride: I pride myself on a job well done!

Cell.Text: Well, words been getting' 'round about how you run things here cap'n.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_BadEnd: How's the crew holdin' up now?

Cell.Text: I'm sorry to say it captain, but they ain't too happy, and they agree somethin' must be done.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_WhatAboutMe: What 'ave my crew been sayin' about me!?

Cell.Text: I'm sorry to say it captain, but they ain't too happy, and they agree somethin' must be done.

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_DoingWhatsBest: I've been doin' what's best for the crew!

Cell.Text: [S] Afraid so cap'n... yer no longer fit for service!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Mutinity: What? Is this mutiny?!

Cell.Text: We've bloody well done it mate! We fought off that creature!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_WonTopic: Gibbs, are we still alive?

Cell.Text: Well bloody done captain!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_NoSweat: Didn't even break a sweat.

Cell.Text: Nor you captain!

Node.Caption: G3_LaS_TheAdventure_Crew: Couldn't have done it without the crew!
